e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/56347/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Inebilizumab, Belimumab, Sutimlimab, Risankizumab, Antilymphocyte immunoglobulin (horse), More', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Lamotrigine, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Oxcarbazepine, Ethotoin, Rufinamide, More', 1767369485);
